      "description": "Affordable, honest transportation with strong value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a budget-friendly option with cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections consistent with its condition, but it remains a practical choice for someone seeking low-cost mobility, a project, or a second vehicle. Priced to move and presented transparently, it\u2019s a sensible chance to get into a vehicle without overspending.",
