    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great opportunity for someone handy, a first-time fixer-upper buyer, or anyone needing a budget-friendly runabout or project. It\u2019s being offered honestly and priced to reflect its condition, with plenty of value for the right person. If you enjoy bringing a car back to life or just want something inexpensive to work with, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 4900.0,
