    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting drivetrain, and good bones for someone who wants dependable transportation or a light project. It shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but it still starts, runs, and drives with the kind of mechanical feel that suggests it has been kept going rather than parked and forgotten. A practical buy for someone who values function over perfection and wants an affordable vehicle with plenty of usable life left.",
      "price": 5900.0,
