    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A gritty, honest machine with real character, this car has the kind of road-worn presence that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates potential\u2014whether you want a budget daily, a hands-on project, or simply a dependable set of wheels with a story to tell. There\u2019s a certain charm here you can\u2019t fake: well-earned patina, classic usability, and the chance to make it your own without breaking the bank.",
      "price": 6900.0,
