      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers practical transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age and will best suit a buyer looking for dependable basic use, a starter vehicle, or a project with potential. A smart value for someone who wants maximum affordability without overpaying.",
      "price": 4950.0,
