      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest budget-friendly car that\u2019s priced to move. It\u2019s in rough shape cosmetically and mechanically, so please don\u2019t expect a showroom ride\u2014but if you need an inexpensive runabout, a project, or something to tinker with, this could be a great fit. Easy on the wallet and a solid opportunity for the right buyer. Come take a look and see if it works for what you need.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running powertrain, dependable cold starts, and good oil pressure. It shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but the chassis feels usable and the mechanicals are straightforward, making it a great option for someone who wants practical transportation or a platform to sort and improve over time. Tracks down the road well, brakes pull it up confidently, and it has the kind of simple, serviceable character that\u2019s getting harder to find. If you\u2019re looking for an affordable used car with honest bones and plenty of life left for the next owner willing to give it a little attention, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
